<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>853</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhè tiáo lù wǒ men dōu méi yǒu zǒu guò, zhǔ yé sū qīn qiè de gào sù wǒ.
 jiān nán de rì zi bù yào tuì hòu, wēi xiǎn de shí hòu tā bì dā jiù wǒ.
 jiù zhè yàng zǒu guò nán wàng de suì yuè, tā de shuāng shǒu shí shí chān fú zhe.
 cái yǒu wǒ men jīn tiān de xiāng féng, shí jià lù shàng tóng chàng yī shǒu gē.
 lái a wǒ men xiàng shén jìng bài, tā gěi de ēn huì zhēn shì tài duō tài duō.
 wǒ men dōu bù zhī dào míng tiān de dào lù, wǒ men shēn xìn tā shì yǐn dǎo zhě.</lyrics>
<title>zhè tiáo lù wǒ men dōu méi yǒu zǒu guò 迦南853</title>
</song>